data.description: Fabulous setting for this 4 bed 2.5 bath home. Seasonal lake view. Remodeled kitchen with granite countertops and breakfast bar. Keeping room with fireplace. Primary bedroom with nice sitting area. Remodeled bathroom has soaking tub, double vanities and walk-in closet. The private in-ground pool is ready for summer fun. Also terraced beds for the garden of your choice. Great combination of nice landscaping and natural beauty. Peaceful southern charm.
